Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.03,0:00:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is Yuma Tsukumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm a first year middle school student, aiming to bring it to 'em to become the Duel Champion one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eh? You're giving me Baby Tragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't that an Exceed Monster?--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't, Yuma! Accepting Tokunosuke's card like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That guy's action definitely has hidden motives!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You guys are a little too distrusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you were still deceived in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you lose this duel, as a result of the Ante Rule,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Numbers cards will be taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why would you do this? Tokunosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought we were friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.19,0:00:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aspiring Emperor - Hope was... taken away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it, conversely!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.07,0:00:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as this continuous trap card, Uratora C is on my side of the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This duel is mine for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I win, as promised, I'll be taking your Aspiring Emperor - Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're after my Number, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tokunosuke...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.47,0:01:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure what's happening, but my body is surging with energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.98,0:01:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening..?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took one of the Numbers away, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.01,0:01:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the Numbers!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.95,0:01:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. 39! Aspiring Emperor - Hope's number...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokunosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-my body is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's with these steams of light...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we fail to win this Duel, then I will disappear.... from this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me this guy is going to disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I accepted his duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and end your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I have to win this duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Numbers can defeat other Numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now my only other Numbers are,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.87,0:02:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revise Dragon and Terabyte.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On my side of the field are my Level 4 Gagaga, and Level 2 Full Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With these two, I won't be able to Exceed Summon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I see you've prepared yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the victory in one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attack Full Elf with Aspiring Emperor - Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope Sword Slash !!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, our life points are 2500 VS. 1900.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tables has turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one monster in face down defense position.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't quickly summon my own Numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate it'll be all over..!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this I can summon a Numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon my Level 3 monster, Rai-Rider!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I activate Gagaga Magician's monster effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once per turn before the end phase, this card's level can change to anything between 1 to 8!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I change Gagaga Magician to Level 3, the same level as Rai-Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I overlay my Level 3 monsters, Gagaga Magician and Rai-Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With these two monsters, I construct the Overlay network!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:03:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exceed Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear! Numbers 17, Revise Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Numbers 17...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are other Numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case this one is mine too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate my Continuous Trap card!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hidden Mist!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's happening? This fog...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the fog of betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continuous Trap Hidden Mist's effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a monster is special summons to the opponent's side of the field, gain control of that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revise Dragon is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding right? Revise Dragon too..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral..!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether it's rainy, or windy,\N or a cold winter blizzard, or the burning sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they're all ingredients to color each day. \NDon't lose heart, will or love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The kindness you gave me was strict,\N when we clashed I learned irritation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It starts by recognizing our differences, dancing freely,\N the creation of Heaven and Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The truth is, I was lonely. Until I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I lied to myself that being alone was easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My favorite books and hobbies,\N they don't seem to match.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were the only one to nod in agreement with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happiness and sadness and anger and\N Do and Re and Mi and Fa and So and La and Ti and Do,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't work unless they're different,\N the harmony and the scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:06:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one is exactly the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because that's the reason for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if the sounds are dissonant from time to time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}don't give up on the strength that will get you through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When we reach the edge of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the view we see will be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether it's rainy, or windy,\N or a cold winter blizzard, or the burning sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're all ingredients to color each day.\N Don't lose heart, will or love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the kindness you gave me was strict,\N when we clashed I learned irritation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It starts by recognizing our differences, dancing freely,\N the creation of Heaven and Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, with both Hope and Revise stolen away!\NThis is a duel he can't afford to lose!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Numbers 6:\N The Treacherous Numbers!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, these photos are fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're just pasted onto some edited photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one too...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.44,0:07:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they were all photo manipulations?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way we can prove Yuma's innocence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, who would do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Taichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi-kun might know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be, that Taichi was in on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.69,0:07:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kotori.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hold on and listen to me for a sec,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got cut off...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind his voice, we can hear the sound of the school bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's talking to himself again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:07:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time you accepted that you've lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for falling for the trap, you have no one to blame but yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.35,0:08:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must you deceive others around you just to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of thing? Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dueling is meaningless if you're not the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this is the rule of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this more than anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was when I first started dueling...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? So Toku-chan's starting to duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you let us teach you how to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we're playing with Ante Rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ante Rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a gambling duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner takes the loser's cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, you'll be able to duel seriously and get better real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just looking out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was all lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.15,0:08:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Day after day, those guys kept taking my cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot, didn't even realize he's getting ripped off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to him, we got some nice cards..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, I realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has a hidden flipside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys putting up a smiling face just to get close to me, they're always hiding something. Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, I'll pursue the hidden side of the world to its fullest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokunosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's definitely somewhere at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I vowed to use that hidden world to bring them my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to master the sleight of hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I practiced hard everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I took back the cards that were taken from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hated, but I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, everything in this world has a hidden side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I won, everyone obediently wagged their tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is human nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The true nature of society and such,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lie and deceive if you can't win,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same thing with dueling, winning means everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not dueling at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winning is everything, and such...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dueling is the clash between soul and soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's how you're gonna put it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can live forever like a hopeless loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good, he's not around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.93,0:10:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The remaining place we haven't looked is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old gym!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the place for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Taichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever's behind this, I'll definitely get it out of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just... Just a little bit more left...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you guys have to come over?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew you were working on a dominoes line...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why have dominoes in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I set all of this up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokunosuke said he'll give me an Exceed Monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I set this up by morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tokunosuke!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was Tokunosuke's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only Numbers I have left is Terabyte.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll use this Magic card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release Lease - when there's only one monster on my side of the field, I can release that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I can add one Level 3 monster from the deck to my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll release Baby Tragon!...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby Tragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect it..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect it..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby Tragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Baby Tragon can't beat the Numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby Tragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change Baby Tragon to defense position!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I set one card faced down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to harden your defense, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn !!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:12:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw !!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Yuma, where did he run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go check the shopping mall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Revise Dragon's monster effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once per turn, by consuming one Overlay unit, its Attack power is increased by 500!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I flip summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flip summon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a face down defense position monster is changed to face up attack position by the player.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words-- Even if it wasn't attacked, its flip effect can still be activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.91,0:13:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uragutan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Uragutan's flip effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defense position monsters are switched to attack position!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby Tragon is changed back to attack position?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I use Revise Dragon to attack Baby Tragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Stream !!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate my trap card, Half Unbreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half Unbreak - One monster on my side of the field cannot be destroyed by battle this turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, the battle damage to the player is decreased by half.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've been hiding a trap like that..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Aspiring Emperor Hope's attack power is 2500.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half of that damage is plenty enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Aspiring Emperor Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope Sword Slash !!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I activate magic card Book of Reversal from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:15:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this card, one of my flip effect monsters is changed to face down defense position.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way I can reuse its flip effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this keeps up, even if I change Baby Tragon to defense position,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uragutan's flip effect will change it back to attack position,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll take battle damage..!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great that you finally realized this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you only have 300 life points remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next turn it'll be all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori, Tetsuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, just what in the world is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The outcome is already certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2500 VS. 300 ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how did Aspiring Emperor Hope and Revise Dragon end up on Tokunosuke's field...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With 300 life points, I don't have a choice..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do but to defend!...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw !!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Needle Swordsman..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use... at this rate I can't keep defending!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you didn't get the card you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate I'm not even off the ground, and it'll be all over..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how you feel, it's still no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On your side of the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have an Exceed Monster from the bottom of the trash barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rank 1 Baby Tragon, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing you can possibly do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way out, isn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy, why Baby Tragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is..!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby Tragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon Needle Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack power 300?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can a card like that possibly do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly can, together with Baby Tragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That card from the trash can?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll rise to the sky !!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Baby Tragon's monster effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By consuming one overlay unit, one Level 1 monster can attack directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Needle Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Tokunosuke directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merely 300 points of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can barely even feel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Needle Swordsman's monster effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurricane-!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Needle Swordsman direct attacks successfully,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of your face up Magic and Trap cards are returned to the hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:17:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cards that took away Aspiring Emperor Hope and Revise Dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since they're no longer on your field,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two will come back to me once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Numbers, they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got the Numbers back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revise Dragon, attack that face down defense position monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, this is suppose to be my duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Revise Dragon !!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack that face down defense position monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Stream !!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! this way there's no more defending monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aspiring Emperor Hope, direct attack!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go !!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope Sword Slash !!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright !!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it !!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We protected the Numbers cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing! It's not like I did it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an awesome reversal finish, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.17,0:20:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Baby Tragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokunosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your card, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As an exchange, don't use it for underhanded tricks anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby Tragon will be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you're pretty powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Specially, you're the first guy I've ever seen that use flip effects this well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. I'm not falling for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flattering me like that, what's your real intention?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intention? There isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really thought you were powerful! That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:20:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma--!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calling me powerful and all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time ever!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone always called me shameless and dirty..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided. You can keep the card!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a token of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a bunch, Tokunosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, we'll become trusted bros!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.68,0:21:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of this because he got a card, what a greedy guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Returning a desired card...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.73,0:21:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Observation result #9.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Yuma thinks of thing on the flipside..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.73,0:22:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec? you're kidding right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.61,0:22:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's duel! This week's question:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.93,0:22:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Rai-Rider attacks the defense position Chuubone, can it be destroyed? Or not destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.19,0:22:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today's test is hard. I can't divide myself from pleasure and temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanna watch TV when I get home.\N The recent anime are fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.91,0:23:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In any case, this test is hard. \NLanguage, Math and English are especially bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.41,0:23:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm only average at science and social studies.\N The only thing I'm good at is P.E.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.59,0:23:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Wait up, Baby!) For who's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.29,0:23:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Is that, Baby!) ...am I remembering...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.73,0:23:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Just hold on, Baby!) ...the answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(What are we!? Baby!) ...they wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I write the correct answer on this paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.70,0:23:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in one year, in ten years, will anything change?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.44,0:23:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The world I drew in the corner of my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}one day I will race through the open sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.32,0:23:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one can blame this heart of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing is really correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ESPer Robin is coming to our town!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Robin's actor, Fuuya is suffering.
